@startuml
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Chức năng hủy gói hội viên

actor "Người dùng" as User
boundary "_SubscriptionScreenState" as SubscriptionScreenState
control "TokenStorageService" as TokenStorageService
control "PaymentApiService" as PaymentApiService
control "SubscriptionController" as SubscriptionController
control "SubscriptionServiceImpl" as SubscriptionServiceImpl
control "SecurityContextHolder" as SecurityContextHolder
database "ClientRepository" as ClientRepository
database "SubscriptionRepository" as SubscriptionRepository
control "Navigator" as Navigator

User -> SubscriptionScreenState: 1: bấm Hủy hội viên
activate SubscriptionScreenState

SubscriptionScreenState -> SubscriptionScreenState: 2: _cancelMembership()
activate SubscriptionScreenState

SubscriptionScreenState -> TokenStorageService: 3: gọi
activate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService -> TokenStorageService: 4: getToken()
activate TokenStorageService
deactivate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService --> SubscriptionScreenState: 5: trả về kết quả
deactivate TokenStorageService

SubscriptionScreenState -> PaymentApiService: 6: gọi
activate PaymentApiService
PaymentApiService -> PaymentApiService: 7: unsubscribe(token)
activate PaymentApiService

PaymentApiService -> SubscriptionController: 8: gọi API DELETE /subscription
activate SubscriptionController
SubscriptionController -> SubscriptionController: 9: unsubscribe()
activate SubscriptionController

SubscriptionController -> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 10: gọi
activate SubscriptionServiceImpl
SubscriptionServiceImpl -> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 11: unsubscribe()
activate SubscriptionServiceImpl

SubscriptionServiceImpl -> SecurityContextHolder: 12: gọi
activate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder -> SecurityContextHolder: 13: getContext().getAuthentication().getName()
activate SecurityContextHolder
deactivate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder --> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 14: trả về kết quả
deactivate SecurityContextHolder

SubscriptionServiceImpl -> ClientRepository: 15: gọi
activate ClientRepository
ClientRepository -> ClientRepository: 16: findByEmailAndActive(email, true)
activate ClientRepository
deactivate ClientRepository
ClientRepository --> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 17: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientRepository

SubscriptionServiceImpl -> SubscriptionRepository: 18: gọi
activate SubscriptionRepository
SubscriptionRepository -> SubscriptionRepository: 19: findLatestActiveValidSubscription(clientId)
activate SubscriptionRepository
deactivate SubscriptionRepository
SubscriptionRepository --> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 20: trả về kết quả
deactivate SubscriptionRepository

SubscriptionServiceImpl -> SubscriptionRepository: 21: gọi
activate SubscriptionRepository
SubscriptionRepository -> SubscriptionRepository: 22: save(Subscription)
activate SubscriptionRepository
deactivate SubscriptionRepository
SubscriptionRepository --> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 23: trả về kết quả
deactivate SubscriptionRepository

deactivate SubscriptionServiceImpl
SubscriptionServiceImpl --> SubscriptionController: 24: trả về kết quả
deactivate SubscriptionServiceImpl

deactivate SubscriptionController
SubscriptionController --> PaymentApiService: 25: trả về kết quả
deactivate SubscriptionController

deactivate PaymentApiService
PaymentApiService --> SubscriptionScreenState: 26: trả về kết quả
deactivate PaymentApiService

SubscriptionScreenState -> SubscriptionScreenState: 27: _loadData()
activate SubscriptionScreenState

SubscriptionScreenState -> TokenStorageService: 28: gọi
activate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService -> TokenStorageService: 29: getToken()
activate TokenStorageService
deactivate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService --> SubscriptionScreenState: 30: trả về kết quả
deactivate TokenStorageService

SubscriptionScreenState -> PaymentApiService: 31: gọi
activate PaymentApiService
PaymentApiService -> PaymentApiService: 32: getSubscriptionInfo(token)
activate PaymentApiService

PaymentApiService -> SubscriptionController: 33: gọi API GET /subscription
activate SubscriptionController
SubscriptionController -> SubscriptionController: 34: getSubscriptionInfo()
activate SubscriptionController

SubscriptionController -> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 35: gọi
activate SubscriptionServiceImpl
SubscriptionServiceImpl -> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 36: getSubscriptionInfo()
activate SubscriptionServiceImpl

SubscriptionServiceImpl -> SecurityContextHolder: 37: gọi
activate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder -> SecurityContextHolder: 38: getContext().getAuthentication().getName()
activate SecurityContextHolder
deactivate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder --> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 39: trả về kết quả
deactivate SecurityContextHolder

SubscriptionServiceImpl -> ClientRepository: 40: gọi
activate ClientRepository
ClientRepository -> ClientRepository: 41: findByEmailAndActive(email, true)
activate ClientRepository
deactivate ClientRepository
ClientRepository --> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 42: trả về kết quả
deactivate ClientRepository

SubscriptionServiceImpl -> SubscriptionRepository: 43: gọi
activate SubscriptionRepository
SubscriptionRepository -> SubscriptionRepository: 44: findHistoryByClientId(clientId)
activate SubscriptionRepository
deactivate SubscriptionRepository
SubscriptionRepository --> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 45: trả về kết quả
deactivate SubscriptionRepository

SubscriptionServiceImpl -> SubscriptionRepository: 46: gọi
activate SubscriptionRepository
SubscriptionRepository -> SubscriptionRepository: 47: findLatestActiveValidSubscription(clientId)
activate SubscriptionRepository
deactivate SubscriptionRepository
SubscriptionRepository --> SubscriptionServiceImpl: 48: trả về kết quả
deactivate SubscriptionRepository

deactivate SubscriptionServiceImpl
SubscriptionServiceImpl --> SubscriptionController: 49: trả về kết quả
deactivate SubscriptionServiceImpl

deactivate SubscriptionController
SubscriptionController --> PaymentApiService: 50: trả về kết quả
deactivate SubscriptionController

deactivate PaymentApiService
PaymentApiService --> SubscriptionScreenState: 51: trả về kết quả
deactivate PaymentApiService

deactivate SubscriptionScreenState

SubscriptionScreenState -> Navigator: 52: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 53: pop(context, true)
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> SubscriptionScreenState: 54: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate SubscriptionScreenState

SubscriptionScreenState --> User: 55: điều hướng về màn hình trước và hiển thị trạng thái hội viên đã hủy
deactivate SubscriptionScreenState

@enduml
